AddressInfo.Title: Vojvode Stepe Stepanovica
AddressInfo.AccessComments: RFID Card Not available at Info desk AS described in the Station: you must Go through the "staff only" door directly left after the Main entrance. 1st Floor you find 2 Offices where you get the RFID Chip. No cost - also charging is free. You get the Chip on working days between 7am to 6 pm and can keep IT over night.

GeneralComments: If Car ist parked at charging Point - Just Go to the bar ans ask- IT IS mostly the owners Car as there is only 1 Car per month charging... He removes IT immediately :)
